reviewText: I love these items from vhs tapes. My copy did not work on any dvd player that I own.  That includes Sony, LG, Oppo and Hitachi.  All say "error" or format not supported.  Any suggestions?
Wouldn't work on my dvd player.

This is a good DVD. It goes back and puts you inside of the ole Connie. Godfrey is good in his talking and enjoys flying the bird.
This DVD is worth the price, just to see the airplane fly again.
